definitions.definition: To regret.

definitions.definition: An event undertaken to get money by voluntary contributions for a particular activity, such as equipment for extracurricular sports programs, or to defray laboratory costs (salaries) for research of a cure for a particular disease.

A spade.
To move materials with a shovel.
